26.05.2015

A storage for various plotting functions. Finished simulation (jet) files
should be moved e.g. here for further processing.

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Flavour: jet flavour analysis plotting scripts. Legacy from Aman Abhishek,
imported to work with the jet_simulations -fileset.

Usage (within root command line):
.L Stack.cc+/Plot.cc+/Compare.cc+
Stack("jetfile.root")
Plot("jetfile.root")
Compare("jetfile1.root","jetfile2.root","jetfile3.root","jetfile4.root",
        "jetfile5.root","jetfiel6.root")

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Jetsort: basic analysis for studying jet data.

Usage (within root command line):
.L run(PF)SortedJets.C
run(PF)SortedJets("hists_****.root")

.L runMinimalGraph.C
runMinimalGraph("jets_****.root")

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

PTCut: analysis for detector simulations.

